title: "Quick Start"
description: "Get started quickly"
---

# Quick Start

Follow these steps to get started.
`);

  // Create API overview.md
  fs.writeFileSync(path.join(TEST_DIR, 'docs', 'api', 'overview.md'), `---
title: "API Overview"
description: "API reference documentation"
---

# API Overview

This is the API reference.
`);

  // Create a page without frontmatter (should trigger warning)
  fs.writeFileSync(path.join(TEST_DIR, 'docs', 'guides', 'bad-page.md`), `# Bad Page

This page is missing frontmatter.
`);
}

